    <description>Updated record triggered flow that replaces PB  &quot;CF - Trigger - Update SaaS Onboarding Fields From Combined Funnel Record&quot; and autolaunched flow. Updated 9/6/23 to include Payroll Interest Level field mapping.
01/24/24 - Updated flow to populate additional fields in case Activaion Override is changed on CF. (Process Builder Replacement)
09/20/24 - PE - When retrieving OB, removed logic to look at the OB Funnel Stage. Instead, added a decision node to look at SaaS Date Of Activation to check if the account is activated or not.
03/10/25 - PE - Added nodes to populate Date of SaaS Override on related Onboarding Attempt
9/2/25- DM- Added nodes to populate Date of SaaS Override Denial on related OA if denied by manager</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>forD_DateOfOverride_SaaSActivationOverrideUpdatedOnCF</name>
        <dataType>Date</dataType>
        <expression>IF(
ISCHANGED({!$Record.SaaS_Activation_Override__c}),
TODAY(),
null
)</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>forD_FunnelStageChanged_SaaSActivationOverrideUpdatedOnCF</name>
